23:
Kings will be your foster fathers, and their queens your nursemaids;\q1 they will bow down to you with their faces to the earth and lick the dust of your feet;
\q1 and you will know that I am Yahweh; those who wait for me will not be put to shame."


\q1

25:
But this is what Yahweh says,\q1 "Yes, the captives will be taken away from the warrior, and spoils will be rescued;
\q1 for I will oppose your adversary and save your children.


\q1
